- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is also a likely category as the paper discusses higher-order programs and foundational calculi, which are relevant to programming language theory. 
- cs.TL (Formal Languages and Automata Theory) is another possible category as the paper deals with formal systems and translations between them. 
- cs.SE (Software Engineering) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper discusses a technique for proving termination of programs, which is relevant to software engineering. 
- cs.FL (Formal Methods) is also a less likely category, but still possible as the paper deals with formal systems and their properties.
